column5: hey folks, been a while since ive been on here,hope all is well. my 2year old basically destroyed our laptops keyboard,yanking all the letters off,so its been dificult type anything.  hope to be back on here more now that its fixed.   jason

I had a fella back in Ft. Smith that used to come in every other month or so to have his laptops keyboard replaced for the very same reason.    :rofl2:  Get yourself a USB keyboard to tide you over when this happens.
